thread.title: Ruth Mulcahy
thread.title_full: Inish Pharmacy reviewed by Ruth Mulcahy

author: Ruth Mulcahy
title: Ruth Mulcahy
text: Just used this company for the first time. I am careful but I was encouraged by the large amount of positive reviews posted. I thought it only fair to add my review to the others. The prices were excellent for the products I selected and I saved €3 on 1 item alone which typically retails at €11. I got it for €7.95 on here. The order was delivered promptly and I was communicated with via the courier/company throughout the process. Well done all.
